# {{ .ProjectName }} - NFT Collection & Marketplace

A complete NFT development stack built with [Dokrypt](https://dokrypt.com), featuring an ERC-721 collection, a decentralized marketplace, and EIP-2981 royalty support.

## Architecture

This template includes three core smart contracts:

- **NFTCollection.sol** - A standalone ERC-721 implementation with minting, max supply cap, configurable mint price, and IPFS-based metadata.
- **Marketplace.sol** - A decentralized NFT marketplace supporting listings, purchases, cancellations, and an offer system with a 2.5% platform fee.
- **Royalty.sol** - An EIP-2981 royalty standard implementation with global defaults and per-token overrides.

All contracts are **standalone** with no external dependencies (no OpenZeppelin). They compile with Solidity `^0.8.20`.

