## Quick Start

```bash
# Start the development environment
dokrypt up

# Compile contracts
forge build

# Run tests
forge test -vvv

# Deploy contracts
node scripts/deploy-nft.js

# Upload metadata to IPFS
node scripts/upload-metadata.js
```

